      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. NAKITA (6) is overdue for a maiden success having placed at six of 13 starts and finishing in the money again at Warragul. Although beaten was on pace and game in defeat. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Rates highly and will give a great sight. DR. HOUDINI (2) turned in a moderate run last time when sixth at Warragul over 400m behind Jumbuk Eileen (24.37) in a Bottom Up - Maiden. One of the main contenders. MACALISTER ABBY (1) boxed on the inside and gets chance to find form. Last time finished 5th in a Bottom Up - Maiden on July 8 over 435m at Sale behind Blackness Castle beaten 11 lengths (25.35). Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Has ability and is one of the better chances.",
